" Terminal
:tnoremap <Esc> <C-\><C-n>
au BufEnter * if &buftype == 'terminal' | :startinsert | endif
" Toggle 'default' terminal
nnoremap <C-n> :call ChooseTerm("term-slider", 1)<CR>
